    {
      "id": "ea88a990-7333-4d06-9471-a2fc47b757f0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Game-based learning has demonstrated pedagogical effectiveness and recent advancements in sensors and nlp made data acquisiton a whole new ball-game. Due to the requirements of intertaction with a game, GBL is a prime candidate for effectiveness of LA-based early warning systems. ",
