    {
      "id": "b1a5f045-5922-4e9c-a548-12e23db7bcbe",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus authors explore a multi-task and multi-modal learning analytics framework for Game-Based LEarning Environments. Framework is evaluated on 2 distinct student populations (n = 61 and n = 118). The models are tasked with predicting post-test performance and interest. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
